    "description": "投身于一个充满惊喜的世界，每一张翻开的卡牌都可能是你通往胜利或麻烦的门票。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/98a27955ab826fef2ca4a2731f78428f.poster.avif?t=1733958715\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/98a27955ab826fef2ca4a2731f78428f.webm?t=1733958715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/98a27955ab826fef2ca4a2731f78428f.mp4?t=1733958715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>序章展示了神秘森林的一部分，这个森林在每次游戏中都会发生变化。你能掌握战略性翻牌的艺术，揭开故事的第一个谜团吗？在这个引人入胜的roguelike体验中，尝试一场结合了战术思维、运气和探索的大冒险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/83e27602262c3ddb350b4508cd3674d8.poster.avif?t=1733958715\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/83e27602262c3ddb350b4508cd3674d8.webm?t=1733958715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/83e27602262c3ddb350b4508cd3674d8.mp4?t=1733958715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >序章特点：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>战略战斗：玩一个每个选择都很重要的游戏。学会明智地选择你的卡牌，仔细规划你的攻击。<br></li><li>Roguelike元素：发现收集卷轴如何让你变得更强大。<br></li><li>生动的世界：探索具有美丽图像的充满氛围的森林的一部分。<br></li><li>卡牌：尝试有限的卡牌集，让你体验完整游戏的多样性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/d63620f324a10bcfced0a2ef9cd949c9.poster.avif?t=1733958715\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/d63620f324a10bcfced0a2ef9cd949c9.webm?t=1733958715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/d63620f324a10bcfced0a2ef9cd949c9.mp4?t=1733958715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>故事的开端：遇见关键人物，发现在完整版中展开的神秘剧情的开始。<br></li><li>可重玩性：由于森林不断变化，序章的每次游戏都提供独特的体验。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/8ceb8f3f9badcf9dfaa449393c3c7b75.poster.avif?t=1733958715\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/8ceb8f3f9badcf9dfaa449393c3c7b75.webm?t=1733958715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139190/extras/8ceb8f3f9badcf9dfaa449393c3c7b75.mp4?t=1733958715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>尝试游戏元素，<i>杀戮尖塔、影铸</i>和类似的基于卡牌的roguelike游戏的粉丝们会发现既熟悉又新鲜。",
